{"tid":1537002,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[極重要] 香港01借直播為名為警方提供証據 + 破解法","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:40:03.000Z","uid":164565,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b29663a2ed287aa45b4cb3ee057cf0b4d4dee834","tid":1537002,"uid":164565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:50:17.000Z","msg":"9日3日，垃圾香港01跟住抗爭者快閃，跟到<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上埋巴士</span></span></strong>仲<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一直開住cam記錄</span></span></strong>，之後無論做咩都記錄哂，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">狗狗仲根據直播內容搵到架巴士，捉左29人</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/votqj64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvotqj64.png&h=91840c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攻略法<br />\n1. 有cam嘅情況下絕唔可以上巴士，因為好易追蹤到你同埋<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一定走唔到</span></strong><br />\n2. 快閃要走時，最好捐晒明顯嘅gear被人，搵定個好嘅收賣佬，之後改變主意叫佢被返你。好處係當唔好彩被狗狗咬到時，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>證明唔到你出現過咩地方</strong></span>"},{"pid":"044c2dbc3233f36a6feb144fe18530ac7233f90c","tid":1537002,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:50:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /